        <detaileddescription>
<para>The Virtual Capture stream is a stereo stream capturing the combined audio output mix of the capture-eligible sounds (typically app-generated) currently being played by the audio rendering engine. The &apos;format&apos; argument must be populated with the correct settings for virtual capture, which uses a channel count of 2 and a sample rate of 48,000.</para>
